Themes # A theme changes the global skin of Sublime Text 3. It changes the tabs, side bar, quick panels (goto, command palette), status bar, etc&hellip;
Here&rsquo;s a non-exhaustive list of themes (top 100):
Predawn Material Theme Theme - Spacegray Seti_UI Theme - Brogrammer Theme - Flatland Theme - Soda Note: the convention for the theme packages name is that they start with Theme -.
